<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
    <head>
        <!-- Required meta tags #374355 -->
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
        <meta name="author" content="Simon" />
        <meta name="copyright" content="©2019 WPSsimply">
        <meta name="description" content="WPSsimply - Relation entre fournisseurs et entrepôt" >
        {% block SEO %}
        {% endblock %}
        <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://bootswatch.com/4/lux/bootstrap.min.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/styles.css">
        {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
        <title>WPS | {% block title %}{% endblock %}</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="{{ uri("home") }}"><span class="color-title">WPS</span>simply.</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarColor02" aria-controls="navbarColor02" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarColor02">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ uri("home") }}">Accueil</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ uri("warehouses_all") }}">Entrepôts</a>
						</li>
						<li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ uri("products_all") }}">Produits</a>
						</li>
						<li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ uri("suppliers_all") }}">Fournisseurs</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="navbar-nav">
                        {% if not session.auth %}
                        <li class="nav-item"><a href="{{ uri("login") }}" class="btn btn-outline-info">Sign In</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a href="{{ uri("register") }}" class="btn btn-outline-warning">Sign Up</a></li>
                        {% else %}
                        <li class="nav-item"><a href="{{ uri("profile") }}" class="btn btn-warning text-dark">Mon profil</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a href="{{ uri("logout") }}" class="btn btn-outline-danger">Log Out</a></li>
                        {% endif %}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </header>

        <main class="container mt-5">
        {% for success in flash("success") %}
		<div class="alert alert-success text-center col-4 offset-4 mt-2 mb-5" role="alert">
			{{ success }}
		</div>
		{% endfor %}

		{% for errors in flash("alert") %}
		<div class="alert alert-danger text-center col-4 offset-4 mt-2 mb-5" role="alert">
			{{ errors }}
		</div>
		{% endfor %}

        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
        </main>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="font-small pt-4 bg-primary">
            <div class="container-fluid text-center text-md-left">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 mt-md-0 mt-3">
                        <h5 class="text-uppercase text-white"><span class="text-warning">WPS</span>simply</h5>
                        <p>Can you make it pop this looks perfect. Just Photoshop out the dog, add a baby, and make the curtains blue make it sexy, I think we need to start from scratch.</p>
                        <p>The right info at the right time to the right people shelfware, so upstream selling but circle back and quarterly sales are at an all-time low. What are the expectations churning anomalies regroup. </p>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="clearfix w-100 d-md-none pb-3">
                    <div class="col-md-3 mb-md-0 mb-3">
                        <h5 class="text-uppercase text-white">Links</h5>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li><a href="#!" class="text-warning">Link 1</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#!" class="text-warning">Link 1</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#!" class="text-warning">Link 1</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#!" class="text-warning">Link 1</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3 mb-md-0 mb-3">
                        <h5 class="text-uppercase text-white">Links</h5>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li><a href="#!" class="text-warning">Link 1</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#!" class="text-warning">Link 1</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#!" class="text-warning">Link 1</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#!" class="text-warning">Link 1</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-copyright text-center py-3">© 2019 Copyright:
                <a href="/" class="text-white"> WPSsimply.com</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-copyright text-center py-3"><a href="{{ uri('legal_notices') }}" class="text-white">Mentions légales</a></div>
        </footer>
        <!-- Footer -->
        {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/parallax/3.1.0/parallax.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>